Introduction

Sitala is a Thai singer. She was a member of the girl group H1-KEY. She is the daughter of Thai actor Sarunyu Wongkrachang and has a twin sister.

She debuted as a member of H1-KEY on January 5, 2022 with their first single "Athletic Girl".

On May 25, 2022 GLG announced that Sitala decided to leave the group for personal reasons.
